<title>Chamber of Mines of SA: The Science of Gold Extraction</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#0000A0">

<p align="center"><font color="#008040" size="5"><strong>THE
SCIENCE OF GOLD EXTRACTION</strong></font></p>

<p align="center"><font color="#0080FF" size="5"><em><strong>A
Brief South African History</strong></em></font></p>

<p align="center"><font color="#0000A0" size="3"><strong>October
1996</strong></font></p>

<hr noshade width="60%">

<p align="center"><font color="#FF0000" size="4"><strong>CONTENTS</strong></font></p>

<blockquote>
    <blockquote>
        <blockquote>
