<p><font FACE="Arial"><font color="#000080"><sub>By contrast, at current production levels, known oil and gas reserves are equivalent to 43 and 66 years respectively. 70% of reserves of 
oil and gas in the Middle East and the CIS.</font></sub></font> </p>
