<p align=center><font color="#008040">&#160;<font size=5><b>THERE'S A BRIGHT FUTURE IN THE MINING INDUSTRY</b></font><font size=4><b> </b></font></font></p>
<p align=center><font color="#0080FF"><font size=5><em><b><tt>CAREER OPTIONS</tt></b></em></font></font></p>
<p align=center><font color="#008040"><font size=5><em><b><tt><img src="../images/linegr.gif" align=bottom width=402 height=5></tt></b></em></font></font></p>
