<A HREF="/res1.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/tb102.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="Resources"></A>
<A HREF="/kruger.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/tb104.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="Krugerrand"></A>
<A HREF="/new.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/tb105.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="What's New?"></A>
<A HREF="/info.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/tb106.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="Contacting us"></A>
