<A NAME = "MINERALS"></A><hr>
<center><h3>Minerals Mined in South Africa</h3><br>
Andalusite, Andesite, Antimony, Asbestos, Brentonite, Calcite, Chrome, Coal, Cobalt, Copper, Diamonds, Dolomite, Dolorite, Feldspar, Fluorspar, Gold, Granite, Iron Ore, Kaolin, Laterite, Limestone, Magnesite, Manganese, Mica, Morite, Montmorillonite, Nickel, Osmium, Palladium, Perlite, Platinum, Quartzite, Rhodium, Semi-precious Stones, Silica, Silver, Sulphur, Talc, Tin, Titanium, Uranium, Vanadium, Verdite,Vermiculite, Zinc, Zirconium.<br><p>
<br><center>

<a href="/main.htm"> <IMG SRC="/images/nb1.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE border=0 alt="Main Menu" hspace=20></a>
<a href="#top"> <IMG SRC="/images/nb2.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE border=0 alt="Top of Page" hspace=20></a>
<a href="#toolbar"> <IMG SRC="/images/nb3.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE border=0 alt="Toolbar" hspace=20></a>
</center><br><br><br><br><br>
