<p align=center><font color="#804040"><font size=6>CELEBRATING THE CENTENARY<br>
OF THE SCHOOL OF MINES<br>
<img src="wits.gif" alt="WIts University" align=bottom width=100 height=138></font></font></p>
<div align=center><center>
