<p align=center><font color="#FF0000"><font size=4><strong><tt>All articles reproduced with the kind permission of<br>
</tt></strong></font></font><img src="../images/Arena1.jpg" alt="Arena: The Quarterly Magazine for Alumni and Friends of the University of the Witwatersrand" align=bottom width=405 height=80></p>
<p><font size=4>The History of the </font><a href="http://sunsite.wits.ac.za/wits/wits1.html"><font size=4>University of the Witwatersrand</font></a><font size=4> is inextricably bound up with the development of 
the mining industry in South Africa and so it is fitting that in this centenary year of the School of 
Mines, we should dedicate an issue of ArenA to celebrating this association.</font></p>
