<LI><A HREF="http://www.info-mine.com/assoc-inst/cim/Welcome.html">Canadian Institute of Mining Metallurgy and Petroleum</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.mineralswa.asn.au/">Chamber of Mines and Energy of Western Australia</a>
<li><A HREF="http://harold.eastky.com/coa/">Coal Operators & Associates, Incorporated</a>
<li><a href="http://204.191.204.2/www/0/sn0004/EMCBC/">Environmental Mining Council of British Columbia</a>
<li><a href="http://www.metal.ntua.gr/msslab/MineSim96/euromines.html#eurom">European Association of Metals</a>: (EUROMETAUX)
<LI><A HREF="http://www.umanitoba.ca/geosci/GAC/gac.html">Geological Association of Canada</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.bris.ac.uk/depts/geol/gig/gig.html">Geoscience Information Group (UK Geological Society)</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.aescon.com/geosociety/index.html">Geological Society of America</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.goldinstitute.com/">Gold Institute, The</a> 
