<LI><A HREF="http://www.iza.com/">International Zinc Association</a>: (IZA)
<li><A HREF="http://www.miningusa.com/associat/kca/kca.htm">Kentucky Coal Association (KCA)</a>
<li><A HREF="http://www.coaleducation.org/kcmec/kcmec.htm">Kentucky Coal Marketing and Export Council</A>
<li><A HREF="http://www.miningusa.com/kmi/kmi.htm">Kentucky Mining Institute</a>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.minerals.org.au/draft.htm">Minerals Council of Australia</a>: (MCA)
<LI><A HREF="http://www.tms.org/">Minerals, Metals & Materials Society, The </A>
<li><a href=http://www.umanitoba.ca/geosci/CANMIN/mac.html>Mineralogical Association of Canada</a>
