<li><A HREF="http://www.metc.doe.gov/projfact/power/pfbc/fourriv.html">Clean Coal Technology Demonstration Program</A>
<li><A HREF="http://www.epri.com/">Electric Power Research Institute (EPRI)</A>
<li><A HREF="http://www.state.ky.us/edc/cmec.htm">Kentucky Coal Marketing and Export Council</A>
<li><A HREF="http://www.miningusa.com/educat~1/KCFBOOK.htm">Kentucky Coal Facts Book</a>
