MBEKI TO UNVEIL GROWTH/DEVELOPMENT STRATEGY<I> (Business Day , Jhb)</I><BR>
A team appointed by SA's Deputy President Thabo Mbeki has designed a growth and development strategy which aims to propel the country's economy to a sustainable growth path averaging 6% a year by the turn of the century.<BR><P>
DE BEERS DETAILS RUSSIAN GEM DEAL<I> (Business Day)</I><BR>
De Beers Centenary has won from the Russian diamond industry exclusive rights for its Central Selling Organisation to market its products, including 80% of the non run of mine diamonds, previously the source of unofficial leaks into the international markets.  A memorandum to this effect was signed on Friday.<BR><P>
