The great sell-off on the financial markets entered its fifth day yesterday, with excited traders warning that SA could be on the road to a Mexico-style implosion.<BR><P>
FREEGOLD DEAL TO INCREASE PROFITABILITY<I>(Business Report)</I><BR>
The full calendar operations (Fulco) agreement entered into between Free State Consolidated Gold Mines and seven unions and associations was aimed at ensuring Freegolds problematic shafts become profitable again.<BR><P>
