<TITLE>Chamber of Mines of South Africa: Mining News</TITLE></head>
 <BODY  BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000080"><Center><b><center><b><b><font size=4>THURSDAY, 19  DECEMBER 1996 - at 11H00 GMT+2 </font></b></b></center></center><BR>

DE BEERS INCREASES PRESSURE ON RUSSIA <I>(Business Day, Jhb.)</I><BR>
