USE OF SUBSIDIES TO OVERHAUL MINE HOSTEL SYSTEM UNDER DISCUSSION <I>(Business Day, Jhb.)</I><BR>
Govt is in talks with the Chamber of Mines and NUM on a proposal to use institutional housing subsidies to overhaul the mine hostel system.<BR><P>
