	<B><Center><A HREF="http://www.woza.co.za">http://www.woza.co.za</A></Center></B>
for a piece by Ciaran Ryan on Marxism & business in SA as well as immediate past president of the Chamber of Mines,  At du Plessiss address in Spokane - Ed.
</I><BR><P>
