<TITLE>First International Symposium on Mine Simulation via the Internet</TITLE>
<CENTER><BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff" TEXT="#000080">
<FONT SIZE=7 COLOR=800040><B>MineSim '96</B></FONT>
<h2><b>First International Symposium on <br>Mine Simulation via the Internet</b></h3>
<h5><I>Hosted on this site by</I><br><a href="/main.htm"> THE CHAMBER OF MINES OF SOUTH AFRICA</a><p>
OFFICIAL WEB SITE: <a href="http://www.metal.ntua.gr/msslab/MineSim96/index.html">NATIONAL TECHNICAL UNIVERSITY OF ATHENS</a>
</h5>

<p>
<IMG SRC="/line3.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE><br>
</CENTER><br><p>
<a name="top"></a>
<FONT SIZE=3 COLOR=008000>The University of Idaho (U of I), USA and the National Technical University of Athens
(NTUA), Greece are pleased to announce the 1st International Symposium on Mine
Simulation ever to be held on the Internet.<p>

The Symposium is organized by the Department of Metallurgy and Mining of U of I and
the Department of Mining Engineering and Metallurgy  of NTUA. It is intended that this
symposium will be the first in a series of symposia on system simulation, artificial
intelligence techniques, virtual reality and other related topics, as they apply in mining.<p> </FONT>

<Center>
<TABLE BORDER=1 cellpadding=4>
<TR><Th align=center valign=middle><a href="#PAPERS"> Call for Papers</a></Th>
<Th align=center valign=middle><a href="#topics">Topics</a></Th>
<Th align=center valign=middle><a href="#format">Format</a></Th>
<Th align=center valign=middle><a href="#ORG">Organising Committee</a></Th>
<Th align=center valign=middle><a href="#SPON1">Sponsors</a></Th>
<Th align=center valign=middle><a href="#STAT"> Status Reports</a></Th>
<Th align=center valign=middle><a href="#ABS">Accepted Abstracts</a></Th>
<Th align=center valign=middle><a href="#info">Enquiries</a></th>
</TR>
</table>
</Center>
<p>
<A NAME="info"></A>
<CENTER><b>Please address all enquiries regarding the symposium to:</b></CENTER>
<ul>
<li><A HREF="mailto:sturgul@uidaho.edu"><b>Dr John Sturgal</b></a>, Dept. of Metallurgy and Mining, University of Idaho</CENTER>
<ul>
<li>Telephone:  (208) 885 7939
<li>Facsimile: (208) 885 2855
</ul>
<li><A HREF="mailto:panagiotou@metal.ntua.gr"><b>Dr. George N. Panagiotou</b></a>, Dept. of Mining Engineering, National Technical University of Athens</CENTER>
<ul>
<li>Telephone:  +30 1 7722.198
<li>Facsimile: +30 1 7722.191
</ul>
</ul>
