<a href="#toolbar"> <IMG SRC="/nb3.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE border=0 alt="Toolbar" hspace=20></a>
</center><br><br><p><p><p>

<H4>
<A NAME="ABS">ACCEPTED ABSTRACTS</A></H4>
<pre>
Ambrose, Dean H., Solid Modeling Simulation used as an Alternative Method to
              Study Safety Insures in Mine Elevator/Hoist Systems, U. S. Dept of
              Energy, Pittsburgh, PA USA
              ambrosedh@ptbma.usbm.gov

Arguelles, Luis, Designing new user Interfaces for GPSS/H, CARBONAR, Oviedo, SPAIN
              100126.146@CompuServe.COM

Bascur, O and Kennedy, J. Patrick, The Industrial Desktop in Mining, OSI Software, inc.,
              Houston TX and San Leandro, CA USA
              Osvaldo_A_Bascur/Sales#SALES@notes.oilsystems.com

Brnich, M. J., Glowacki, Mallett, Unger, R. L., and Vaught, Computerized Mine Emergency
              Response Simulation, U. S. D. of Energy, Pittsburgh, PA USA
              unger@ergoserv1.usbm.gov

Coward, J, Analysis of Mine Equipment Condition Monitoring Data, Syncrude, Edmonton,
              Alberta, CANADA
              corard.julian@syncrude.com

Dalkowski, B., T., A Simulation Model for the Machine Rapair-Inventory Assembly
              Problem, Wroclaw Technical Univ., Wroclaw, POLAND
              hardygora@pwr.wroc.pl

